description	"Aurra Sing

Class: Jedi.
Class Summary: 
A versatile melee/gunner/sniper hybrid with force abilities. 

Weaponry:
- Dual Pistols (Based on dual Clone Pistols)
- Czerka Adventurer Rifle *
- Heavy Melee

* Special Weapons Description
--- Czerka Adventurer Rifle
- Based on Projectile Rifle
- Has a faster reload
- Limited ammo (5)

--- Lightsaber
- Defense (1)
- Can use Yellow Style
- Deflect (2)
- Can block force push/pull by blocking

Force Powers:
- Jump (2)
- Push (2)
- Pull (3)
- Speed (2)
- Protect (2)
- Sense (2)

Attributes:
- Heal (1)
- BP Free Jumps

Abilities:
- Poison Darts (3) [Alt Ability 3]

Pain, death and vengeance have been constants in Aurra Sing's life. Had she benefited from a better upbringing, perhaps she may have grown to be one of the greatest of the Jedi order. Instead, she became one its deadliest scourges."